// End RAW data for converting CJK characters


// fallbacks

"| yi < i;"
"| wu < u;"
"| bi < b;"
"| ci < c;"
"| di < d;"
"| fu < f;"
"| gu < g;"
"| he < h;"
"| ji < j;"
"| ku < k;"
"| li < l;"
"| mi < m;"
"| pi < p;"

"| si < s;"

"| wa < w;"
"| xi < x;"
"| yi < y;"
"| zi < z;"

// filter out the half-width hangul
":: [^\uFFBE-\uFFEE] fullwidth-halfwidth ();"
":: (lower) ;"
  }
